/* ripple — click feedback via control's own background-image; ControlEffectsRoot sets --aui-ripple-x/y/r from pointer + toggles data-ripple, keyframes animate the two registered properties the radial-gradient reads.
 * Registration required for interpolation — browsers without @property degrade to a brief static flash, never broken layout. */
